ing containing health claims, warning statements or supplementary information.\"' is not assignable to type '\"Các mặt còn lại của bao bì có chứa health claims, warning statements hoặc thông tin bổ sung.\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/vi.ts","start":28908,"length":107,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'description' which is declared here on type '{ readonly id: \"other\"; readonly label: \"Mặt khác\"; readonly subtitle: \"Other Panels / Back / Side\"; readonly badge: \"Tùy chọn\"; readonly description: \"Các mặt còn lại của bao bì có chứa health claims, warning statements hoặc thông tin bổ sung.\"; readonly mustHave: readonly [...]; readonly avoid: readonly [...]; rea...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":28576,"length":78,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"Back or side panel if it has health claims (\\\"High in Protein\\\", \\\"Low Fat\\\"...)\"' is not assignable to type '\"Mặt sau hoặc mặt bên nếu có health claims (\\\"High in Protein\\\", \\\"Low Fat\\\"...)\"'."},{"start":28656,"length":50,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"\\\"Supplement Facts\\\" panel for dietary supplements\"' is not assignable to type '\"Phần \\\"Supplement Facts\\\" nếu là thực phẩm bổ sung\"'."},{"start":28708,"length":34,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"\\\"Drug Facts\\\" panel for OTC drugs\"' is not assignable to type '\"\\\"Drug Facts\\\" panel nếu là OTC drug\"'."},{"start":28761,"length":61,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"Uploading duplicate images of the same panel multiple times\"' is not assignable to type '\"Upload ảnh trùng lặp cùng một mặt nhiều lần\"'."},{"start":28833,"length":3,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"Health claims like \\\"Fat Free\\\", \\\"Low Sodium\\\", \\\"Excellent Source of...\\\" are all checked under 21 CFR Part 101. If you have claims, always upload this panel.\"' is not assignable to type '\"Health claims như \\\"Fat Free\\\", \\\"Low Sodium\\\